                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/rest/edit/master/knpu/episode2/token-validation.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>It's finally that time: to add a little bit of validation to our token. </p>
<h2 id="how-we-validated-programmer">How We Validated Programmer <a class="headerlink" href="token-validation#how-we-validated-programmer" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>This should start to feel easy because we did all of this before with our 
programmer. Now let me remind you, in the <code>PogrammerController</code>, to 
validate things we call this <code>validate()</code> function, which is something I 
created for this project before we even started:</p>
